Package it.polimi.ingsw.server.model.gameplay

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    DevelopmentCardGrid
    Represents the space where available Development Cards are placed
    DevelopmentCardSpace
    Represents the space where the development cards are placed, divided into 3 decks
    FaithTrack
    Represents the 'Faith Track' on which faith points are counted and on which the pope's tiles are activated and deactivated
    LeaderCardSpace
    Represents the space where all Leader cards assigned to a player are placed
    LorenzoDeMedici
    Represents the opponent in the SinglePlayer game mode
    MarketBoard
    Represents the game's market device
    MVCModel
    MVC Model component
    PersonalBoard
    represents the personal board of the player.
    ProductionPowerRegistry
    The type Production power registry: it's a registry that includes all the active production powers for a specific player .
    StrongBox
    represents the strongbox of resources, from which they can be taken only for productions
    WarehouseDepot
    represents the stock of resources, from which they can be taken for the purchase of development cards or for productions
